title: Cowboys Stalemate Continues
itunes:title: Cowboys Stalemate Continues
description:
Filling in for Colin Cowherd, Doug Gottlieb explains the Jerry Jones-Ezekiel Elliot saga, the horrible field conditions for the Raiders-Packers game, and when Tom Brady will retire. Guests include Urban Meyer, James Harrison, and Geoff Schwartz.
